snippet.title: (REUPLOAD) B3313 1.0 - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
**This only meant for archival purposes**

Basically @chrisrlillo privated almost all B3313 content on his channel, and I just do seem to conveniently have the 1.0 trailer downloaded.

EDIT: I reuploaded this... *𝘳𝘦𝘶𝘱𝘭𝘰𝘢𝘥*, cuz it got copyright claimed due to the song being lisenced, so now song's muted.

Original Description:
Big Shoutouts to Kaze Emanuar for featuring the short version of this trailer on F3! You rock brotha! Also If you haven't noticed yet on last week's stream, i revealed a demo for B3313 1.0, including some new areas and a "castle exclusive to the show" if you will. I know some of you have played it and "kept the secret" so thank you guys, y'all are epic If you wanna check it out, you can download it on the links below. (WARNING FLASHING LIGHTS) https://www.patreon.com/posts/7008704... https://romhacking.com/hack/B13--a-sm... https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-38f... Shoutouts to Taxi Yoshi for the n64 footage Shoutouts to Hornet for Voice Acting (epic bri ish man) Shoutouts to Benedani for Edits and for being such a cool dude. And big shoutouts to The B3313 Team, Contributors and The Cult community, y'all rock! Please consider supporting the channel: https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted... https://streamlabs.com/chrisbrutalagr... https://www.patreon.com/chrisbrutalag... Join The Cult: https://discord.gg/tYCjyk7uCb
